      "id": 2,
      "description": "The atomic cloud arrived over the shores of Tureia in a little more than eight hours after the blast. During the night of June 12th-13th 1971, rain contaminated with radioactive particles began falling on the atoll and its population. This was the worst scenario of all, but while the military knew this very well, the inhabitants were not alerted to the danger. ![](https://fp-nuclear-bucket.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/IMAGE/LEGEND/LEGEND-ENC-2-eng.jpg)",
